OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry
OL,6,Fovernight with lengthy clear spells,
OL,7,Fwhich will allow temperatures to fall,
OL,8,Fgiving the risk of a frost. Some
OL,9,Fpatchy mist and fog is likely to form,
OL,10,Fperhaps with some coastal low cloud.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FEarly mist and fog soon
OL,13,Fclearing, but cloud towards the coast
OL,14,Fmay linger. Sunny spells inland where
OL,15,Fit will be warm, but cool near coasts
OL,16,Fand in northern parts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
